                    <p>
                      Please note that we also offer a 10 day Day Skipper Package course covering 40 hours delivered in our classroom at our shore-based centre followed by 5 days <a class="book-link" href="/courses/rya-day-skipper-practical"><em>RYA Day Skipper Practical Course</em></a> onboard our training yacht, upon request and availability. The Day Skipper package course has a discount of 10%, and can also include VHF course as optional.
